{"title_page": "Kasra Zahedi", "text_new": "{{Infobox person\n| name = Kasra Zahedi\n| image = Kasrazahedipic.jpg\n| image_size = 250px\n| caption = Kasra Zahedi in 2020\n| birth_name = Kasra Zahedimazandarani (Kasra Zahedi)\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1990|05|26}} <ref name=nava>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi Biography | publisher = Kasrazahedi.com | url = https://www.kasrazahedi.com/biography/ }}</ref>\n| birth_place = [[Tehran]],[[Iran]]\n| occupation = {{flatlist|\n*[[Singer]], [[songwriter]], [[musician]]\n}}\n| agent = \n| height = 178cm\n| module = {{Infobox musical artist|embed=yes\n| background = solo_singer\n| genre = {{flatlist|\n*[[Persian pop music|Persian Pop]]}}\n| instrument = {{flatlist|\n*[[Singing|Vocals]], [[Guitar]], [[Piano]]\n}}\n| years_active = 2011 - Present\n\n}}\n}}\n\n'''Kasra Zahedi''' ({{lang-fa|'''\u06a9\u0633\u0631\u06cc \u0632\u0627\u0647\u062f\u06cc'''}}; born May 26, 1990 in [[Tehran]]) is an [[Iranian peoples|Iranian]] [[vocalist]], [[songwriter]], and [[musician]]. <ref name=nava/>\n\n== Early life ==\nKasra Zahedimazandarani with artistic name Kasra Zahedi started [[music]] with a keyboard player at a very young age.<ref name=nava/> \n\nHe is the first child of the family and he has two younger brothers.<ref name=med>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi Iranian singer | publisher = Medium.com | url = https://medium.com/@amirkhani6676/kasra-zahedi-successful-iranian-singer-392b95a0a5fa }}</ref> He is the son of Alireza Zahedi one of the [[veterans]] of the Iran_Iraq [[war]].<ref name=med/> His encourager in [[singing]] was his interest in music and he started [[learning]] [[music]] at a very young age.<ref name=med/>\nIn his [[teens]] he was also interested in [[sports]] in addition to [[music]] and he had a semi-professional career in [[wrestling]] and he has won first place in the [[tournament]] in [[Tehran]] province.<ref name=med/> <ref name=flip>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi Iranian successful singer | publisher = Flipboard | url = https://flipboard.com/article/https%3A%2F%2Fwww.issuewire.com%2Fkasra-zahedi-iranian-successful-singer-1661717478311038 }}</ref>His [[father]] separated from his [[family]] beacause of the [[damage]] caused by the explosion in the [[war]].<ref name=med/><ref name=nava/>\nKasra started [[learning]] [[music]] and singing when he was 10 and his [[favorite]] instrument is [[piano]].<ref name=nava/><ref name=med/><ref name=inter>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi Iranian singer | publisher = interpret news | url = http://interpretnews.com/kasra-zahedi-iranian-successful-singer-481661940959307086 }}</ref>\n\n== Artistic life ==\nKasra zahedi entered the professional world of music since 2007 that is,at the age of 17.<ref name=nilz>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi Biography | publisher = nilz news agency| url = https://nilz.ir/art/14568/biography-kasra-zahrdi }}</ref> <ref name=nava/><ref>[https://musicisho.com/artist/%DA%A9%D8%B3%D8%B1%DB%8C-%D8%B2%D8%A7%D9%87%D8%AF%DB%8C/ \u0632\u0646\u062f\u06af\u06cc \u0647\u0646\u0631\u06cc \u06a9\u0633\u0631\u06cc \u0632\u0627\u0647\u062f\u06cc]</ref> Kasra started [[music]] with a keyboard player without a master and with the help of his hearing aids he would play the [[melodies]] he heard and then at the age of 10 he began to learn principles music and piano under the supervision of Mr Bahrami.<ref name=imdb>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi in IMDB | publisher = IMDB | url = https://imdb.com/name/nm11410021/ }}</ref><ref name=med/><ref name=nava/>\n\nAt the age of 17 kasra and some his friends realised an [[album]] that he had arranged the songs by himself and after two years he made his own solo song And he realised his first solo song in 2014 then he realised songs such as \"ASHEGHE BARON\", \"BAVAR NADARAM\" and \"CHEJORI YADET RAFT\" that people were not very welcomed.<ref name=med/><ref name=nava/><ref name=imdb/><ref name=toptel>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi Singer | publisher = iglobalupdate | url = https://www.iglobalupdate.com/kasra-zahedi-iranian-successful-singer-471661940959307086 }}</ref> \n\nIn 2019 he wrote a song which called \"MOO BE MOO\" for Reza Bahram and this song was nominated for the best title song in [[Hafez Awards|Hafez festival]] and the same year he arranged \"SHABHAYE BAD AZ TO\" song for Reza Bahram for ''Mamnooe'' TV series.<ref name=med/><ref name=nava/><ref name=rza>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi and Reza Bahram In Hafez Awards | publisher = khabaronline | url = https://www.khabaronline.ir/news/1278014/%D8%B1%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%A8%D8%AA-%D9%85%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%86-%DA%86%D8%A7%D9%88%D8%B4%DB%8C-%D8%A8%D8%A7-%D8%B1%D8%B6%D8%A7-%D8%A8%D9%87%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%85-%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D8%A8%D8%AE%D8%B4-%D8%A8%D9%87%D8%AA%D8%B1%DB%8C%D9%86-%D8%AA%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%87-%D8%AA%DB%8C%D8%AA%D8%B1%D8%A7%DA%98-%D8%AC%D8%B4%D9%86 }}</ref><ref name=kasra>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi's song In Hafez Awards | publisher = serat news | url = https://www.seratnews.com/fa/news/467881/%D8%B1%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%A8%D8%AA-%D9%85%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%86-%DA%86%D8%A7%D9%88%D8%B4%DB%8C-%D8%A8%D8%A7-%D8%B1%D8%B6%D8%A7-%D8%A8%D9%87%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%85-%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D8%AC%D8%B4%D9%86-%D8%AD%D8%A7%D9%81%D8%B8 }}</ref>\n\nThe song \"Moo be Moo\" from Reza Bahram with Kasra Zahedi's songwriting and the song \"SHABHAYE BAD AZ TO\" from Reza Bahram with Kasra Zahedi's arrangement used as the title song in ''[[:fa:\u0645\u0645\u0646\u0648\u0639\u0647|Mamnooe]]'' series.<ref name=nava/><ref name=med/><ref name=rza/><ref name=kasra/> It's not the only works of him with famous people in music he also has working for some of the singers such as \"Yasee Binam\" in his career.<ref name=nava/>\n\nIn 2019 he realised a song called \"[https://open.spotify.com/artist/2ArELZJ04ocIhbwQPgtgR3 ZABANAM LAL]\" and after that he announced the contract with Arad Concerct company then he became famous and known between people.<ref name=nava/><ref name=cru>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi best singer in iran | publisher = crunchbase | url = https://www.crunchbase.com/person/kasra-zahedi }}</ref>\n\nOther activities of Kasra Zahedi on official TV of Iran can be mentioned as \"Tarane Baran\" song on channel \"SHOMA\" of IRIB that \"ZABANAM LAL\" song by Kasra Zahedi selected as the best song of the week.<ref name=tv>{{cite web | title = best music of kasra zahedi in IRIB \"SHOMA\" | publisher = telewebion | url = https://www.telewebion.com/episode/2243320 }}</ref>\n\n== Notable works ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! colspan=\"3\" | Singles<ref>{{cite web|url=https://wikiseda.org/Kasra+Zahedi|title=Kasra Zahedi Musics|publisher=wikiseda.com|language=Persian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.radiojavan.com/artist/Kasra+Zahedi|title=Kasra Zahedi Musics|publisher=radiojavan.com|language=Persian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/artist/2ArELZJ04ocIhbwQPgtgR3?si=b3WqxE2DR6Gna1kstS74ZA|title=Kasra Zahedi Musics|publisher=spotify|language=Persian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://ahaang.com/artist/%DA%A9%D8%B3%D8%B1%DB%8C-%D8%B2%D8%A7%D9%87%D8%AF%DB%8C/|title=Kasra Zahedi Musics|publisher=ahaang.com|language=Persian}}</ref>\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! Music name !! Persian !! English\n|-\n|Beyne Ma\n|\u0628\u06cc\u0646 \u0645\u0627\n|Between Us\n|-\n|Asheghe Baroon Bood\n|\u0639\u0627\u0634\u0642 \u0628\u0627\u0631\u0648\u0646 \u0628\u0648\u062f\n|In love with the rain\n|-\n|Bavar Nadaram\n|\u0628\u0627\u0648\u0631 \u0646\u062f\u0627\u0631\u0645\n|I don't believe\n|-\n|Chejoori Yadet Raft\n|\u0686\u062c\u0648\u0631\u06cc \u06cc\u0627\u062f\u062a \u0631\u0641\u062a\n|How did you forget\n|-\n|Joone Mani Akhe\n|\u062c\u0648\u0646 \u0645\u0646\u06cc \u0622\u062e\u0647\n|You're my life\n|-\n|Mahi\n|\u0645\u0627\u0647\u06cc\n|Fish\n|-\n|Zabanam Lal\n|\u0632\u0628\u0627\u0646\u0645 \u0644\u0627\u0644\n|My tongue is mute\n|-\n|Darya Sho\n|\u062f\u0631\u06cc\u0627 \u0634\u0648\n|Become the sea\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n\n==External links==\n{{commons cat|Kasra Zahedi}}\n* {{Instagram|kasrazmusic}}\n* {{Official website|http://www.kasrazahedi.com/}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Zahedi, Kasra}}\n[[Category:1990 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Iranian pop musicians]]\n[[Category:Iranian pop singers]]\n[[Category:Iranian male singers]]\n[[Category:Iranian singer-songwriters]]\n[[Category:Iranian songwriters]]\n[[Category:Iranian composers]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox person\n| name = Kasra Zahedi\n| image = Kasrazahedipic.jpg\n| image_size = 250px\n| caption = Kasra Zahedi in 2020\n| birth_name = Kasra Zahedimazandarani (Kasra Zahedi)\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1990|05|26}} <ref name=nava>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi Biography | publisher = Kasrazahedi.com | url = https://www.kasrazahedi.com/biography/ }}</ref>\n| birth_place = [[Tehran]],[[Iran]]\n| occupation = {{flatlist|\n*[[Singer]], [[songwriter]], [[musician]]\n}}\n| agent = \n| height = 178cm\n| module = {{Infobox musical artist|embed=yes\n| background = solo_singer\n| genre = {{flatlist|\n*[[Persian pop music|Persian Pop]]}}\n| instrument = {{flatlist|\n*[[Singing|Vocals]], [[Guitar]], [[Piano]]\n}}\n| years_active = 2011 - Present\n\n}}\n}}\n\n'''Kasra Zahedi''' ({{lang-fa|'''\u06a9\u0633\u0631\u06cc \u0632\u0627\u0647\u062f\u06cc'''}}; born May 26, 1990 in [[Tehran]]) is an [[Iranian peoples|Iranian]] [[vocalist]], [[songwriter]], and [[musician]]. <ref name=nava/>\n\n== Early life ==\nKasra Zahedimazandarani with artistic name Kasra Zahedi started [[music]] with a keyboard player at a very young age.<ref name=nava/> \n\nHe is the first child of the family and he has two younger brothers.<ref name=med>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi Iranian singer | publisher = Medium.com | url = https://medium.com/@amirkhani6676/kasra-zahedi-successful-iranian-singer-392b95a0a5fa }}</ref> He is the son of Alireza Zahedi one of the [[veterans]] of the Iran_Iraq [[war]].<ref name=med/> His encourager in [[singing]] was his interest in music and he started [[learning]] [[music]] at a very young age.<ref name=med/>\nIn his [[teens]] he was also interested in [[sports]] in addition to [[music]] and he had a semi-professional career in [[wrestling]] and he has won first place in the [[tournament]] in [[Tehran]] province.<ref name=med/> <ref name=flip>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi Iranian successful singer | publisher = Flipboard | url = https://flipboard.com/article/https%3A%2F%2Fwww.issuewire.com%2Fkasra-zahedi-iranian-successful-singer-1661717478311038 }}</ref>His [[father]] separated from his [[family]] beacause of the [[damage]] caused by the explosion in the [[war]].<ref name=med/><ref name=nava/>\nKasra started [[learning]] [[music]] and singing when he was 10 and his [[favorite]] instrument is [[piano]].<ref name=nava/><ref name=med/><ref name=inter>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi Iranian singer | publisher = interpret news | url = http://interpretnews.com/kasra-zahedi-iranian-successful-singer-481661940959307086 }}</ref>\n\n== Artistic life ==\nKasra zahedi entered the professional world of music since 2007 that is,at the age of 17.<ref name=nilz>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi Biography | publisher = nilz news agency| url = https://nilz.ir/art/14568/biography-kasra-zahrdi }}</ref> <ref name=nava/><ref>[https://musicisho.com/artist/%DA%A9%D8%B3%D8%B1%DB%8C-%D8%B2%D8%A7%D9%87%D8%AF%DB%8C/ \u0632\u0646\u062f\u06af\u06cc \u0647\u0646\u0631\u06cc \u06a9\u0633\u0631\u06cc \u0632\u0627\u0647\u062f\u06cc]</ref> Kasra started [[music]] with a keyboard player without a master and with the help of his hearing aids he would play the [[melodies]] he heard and then at the age of 10 he began to learn principles music and piano under the supervision of Mr Bahrami.<ref name=imdb>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi in IMDB | publisher = IMDB | url = https://imdb.com/name/nm11410021/ }}</ref><ref name=med/><ref name=nava/>\n\nAt the age of 17 kasra and some his friends realised an [[album]] that he had arranged the songs by himself and after two years he made his own solo song And he realised his first solo song in 2014 then he realised songs such as \"ASHEGHE BARON\", \"BAVAR NADARAM\" and \"CHEJORI YADET RAFT\" that people were not very welcomed.<ref name=med/><ref name=nava/><ref name=imdb/><ref name=toptel>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi Singer | publisher = iglobalupdate | url = https://www.iglobalupdate.com/kasra-zahedi-iranian-successful-singer-471661940959307086 }}</ref> \n\nIn 2019 he wrote a song which called \"MOO BE MOO\" for Reza Bahram and this song was nominated for the best title song in [[Hafez Awards|Hafez festival]] and the same year he arranged \"SHABHAYE BAD AZ TO\" song for Reza Bahram for ''Mamnooe'' TV series.<ref name=med/><ref name=nava/><ref name=rza>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi and Reza Bahram In Hafez Awards | publisher = khabaronline | url = https://www.khabaronline.ir/news/1278014/%D8%B1%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%A8%D8%AA-%D9%85%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%86-%DA%86%D8%A7%D9%88%D8%B4%DB%8C-%D8%A8%D8%A7-%D8%B1%D8%B6%D8%A7-%D8%A8%D9%87%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%85-%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D8%A8%D8%AE%D8%B4-%D8%A8%D9%87%D8%AA%D8%B1%DB%8C%D9%86-%D8%AA%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%87-%D8%AA%DB%8C%D8%AA%D8%B1%D8%A7%DA%98-%D8%AC%D8%B4%D9%86 }}</ref><ref name=kasra>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi's song In Hafez Awards | publisher = serat news | url = https://www.seratnews.com/fa/news/467881/%D8%B1%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%A8%D8%AA-%D9%85%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%86-%DA%86%D8%A7%D9%88%D8%B4%DB%8C-%D8%A8%D8%A7-%D8%B1%D8%B6%D8%A7-%D8%A8%D9%87%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%85-%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D8%AC%D8%B4%D9%86-%D8%AD%D8%A7%D9%81%D8%B8 }}</ref>\n\nThe song \"Moo be Moo\" from Reza Bahram with Kasra Zahedi's songwriting and the song \"SHABHAYE BAD AZ TO\" from Reza Bahram with Kasra Zahedi's arrangement used as the title song in ''[[:fa:\u0645\u0645\u0646\u0648\u0639\u0647|Mamnooe]]'' series.<ref name=nava/><ref name=med/><ref name=rza/><ref name=kasra/> It's not the only works of him with famous people in music he also has working for some of the singers such as \"Yasee Binam\" in his career.<ref name=nava/>\n\nIn 2019 he realised a song called \"[https://open.spotify.com/artist/2ArELZJ04ocIhbwQPgtgR3 ZABANAM LAL]\" and after that he announced the contract with Arad Concerct company then he became famous and known between people.<ref name=nava/><ref name=cru>{{cite web | title = Kasra Zahedi best singer in iran | publisher = crunchbase | url = https://www.crunchbase.com/person/kasra-zahedi }}</ref>\n\nOther activities of Kasra Zahedi on official TV of Iran can be mentioned as \"Tarane Baran\" song on channel \"SHOMA\" of IRIB that \"ZABANAM LAL\" song by Kasra Zahedi selected as the best song of the week.<ref name=tv>{{cite web | title = best music of kasra zahedi in IRIB \"SHOMA\" | publisher = telewebion | url = https://www.telewebion.com/episode/2243320 }}</ref>\n\n== Notable works ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! colspan=\"3\" | Singles<ref>{{cite web|url=https://wikiseda.org/Kasra+Zahedi|title=Kasra Zahedi Musics|publisher=wikiseda.com|language=Persian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.radiojavan.com/artist/Kasra+Zahedi|title=Kasra Zahedi Musics|publisher=radiojavan.com|language=Persian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/artist/2ArELZJ04ocIhbwQPgtgR3?si=b3WqxE2DR6Gna1kstS74ZA|title=Kasra Zahedi Musics|publisher=spotify|language=Persian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://ahaang.com/artist/%DA%A9%D8%B3%D8%B1%DB%8C-%D8%B2%D8%A7%D9%87%D8%AF%DB%8C/|title=Kasra Zahedi Musics|publisher=ahaang.com|language=Persian}}</ref>\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! Music name !! Persian !! English\n|-\n|Beyne Ma\n|\u0628\u06cc\u0646 \u0645\u0627\n|Between Us\n|-\n|Asheghe Baroon Bood\n|\u0639\u0627\u0634\u0642 \u0628\u0627\u0631\u0648\u0646 \u0628\u0648\u062f\n|In love with the rain\n|-\n|Bavar Nadaram\n|\u0628\u0627\u0648\u0631 \u0646\u062f\u0627\u0631\u0645\n|I don't belive\n|-\n|Chejoori Yadet Raft\